2005-07-05 VZ: multiple config files for sharing options between installations
2005-06-24 VZ: automatically select the viewer best fit for the shown message
2005-05-15 VZ: added autocollecting of addresses in outgoing mail
2005-02-27 VZ: added "Compose|Set if is a reply..." command
2004-09-27 VZ: allow to select "open as mail message" in "Open with" dialog
2004-09-23 VZ: improved UTF-[78] support: try to guess correct encoding
2004-09-18 VZ: implemented support for Python functions in message templates
2004-09-13 VZ: added "Folder|Where is filter..." command
2004-08-13 VZ: "Show MIME Structure" allows to save multiple attachments at once
2004-07-17 VZ: full support for showing PGP/MIME encoded messages
2004-07-17 VZ: added "Send now" command to the composer "Compose" menu
2004-07-16 VZ: show threading indicator in the status column
2004-07-12 VZ: use plain, not encrypted, text in replies to PGP messages
2004-07-11 VZ: integrated DSPAM statistical spam filter
2004-07-06 VZ: "Set From from To" option now behaves more usefully
2004-07-02 VZ: added nop() filter action (stop processing the filter program)
2004-05-15 VZ: added spam filter for dangerous (executable) attachments
2004-05-14 XN: added support for uuencoded attachments
2004-05-12 VZ: fixed bug with slashes and colons not working in the user names
2004-04-22 VZ: improved signature/trailer detection when replying to messages
2004-04-21 VZ: show subfolders not in the tree in bold in browse subfolders dialog
2004-04-20 VZ: added "--import" command line option
2004-04-19 VZ: made "Quick filter" dialog slightly easier to use
2004-04-08 VZ: close the message view window if underlying message is deleted
2004-03-14 VZ: highlight the options with non default values in the options dialog
2004-03-13 VZ: folders can now be dragged in the tree to change their order

